{
  "id": "adv_main_01_08_10",
  "title": "星見編2章15話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_coast-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-3d",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "んん～！ 夜の浜辺って新せ～ん！\n曇りで月明かりもないから、ほんと真っ暗",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mmm! The beach at night is so refreshing!\nThe clouds are hiding the moonlight‚ so it’s pitch dark.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6333.333335071802,
          "startTime": 8.033333335071802
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（遙子さんに誘われるがまま、俺は浜辺にやって来た）\n（大事な話の内容は、聞かされていないままだった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（――Following Haruko-san‚ I find myself at the beach.）\n（I still haven’t heard the important thing she wanted to tell me.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.25061213175456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、でも別に、初めてじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ but it’s not like it’s is our first time here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.583945465087897,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君と\n一緒にここ、夜に歩いたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user} and I\nhave walked here at night before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.18091306090355,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ……あまり、いい思い出ではないですけどね\n確か遙子さんが、オーディションに落ちた日……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right… although it’s not a very good memory.\nI remember it was the day you failed the audition.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.524489784240735,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "そう……それと、麻奈ちゃんが\n初めて挑戦したオーディションに……合格した日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… and the day that Mana-chan‚\non her first attempt… passed her first audition.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.25782311757407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "…………っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ugh",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.22448978424074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "あの日の私、どうしても結果に納得できなくて……\n暗くなってもこの辺でボーッとしてたんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just couldn’t accept the results that day.\nI stood around here staring into the distance‚ even after it got dark.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.25782311757409,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さんから探してこいって言われた時は\nほんとに驚きましたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was really surprised when Saegusa-san\ntold me to go look for you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.65782311757408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "あはは……ごめんね\n私もあの後怒られたから、おあいこで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha… Sorry about that.\nI got scolded afterward as well‚ so I guess we’re even.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.97718518575035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "でも今なら\nあの時のオーディションの結果には納得できるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But right now‚\nI can accept the outcome of that audition.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "どんなに努力を重ねても届かないものってある\n逆に、すぐに届いちゃう人もいるんだ、って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You just can’t reach some things‚ no matter how hard you try.\nMeanwhile‚ there are others who can reach it immediately.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.64385185241701,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "それってもう、向き不向きなんだと思う\n努力している目標に、そもそも素質があるかどうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Some people are just better at some things.\nWhether or not you have the right qualities for what you’re striving for.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.97718518575034,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "あの時、一発でオーディションに受かった\n麻奈ちゃんには、アイドルとしての素質があった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana-chan had the right qualities to be an idol‚ and\nthat’s why she passed the audition on her first attempt.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.14385185241701,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "でも……私には足りなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… I lacked those qualities.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.27882541247779,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "俺はそんなことないと思ってます\n遙子さんにだって素質はある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t agree with that.\nYou have your own qualities as an idol‚ Haruko-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.71215874581112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "素質が花開くのは、早い人もいれば遅い人もいる\nだから遙子さんも――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sometimes‚ those qualities just blossom later than others.\nSo‚ Haruko-san――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.57882541247784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "……でももし、私が……自分で自分の素質を\n信じることができない、って言ったら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But……what if I told you\nI don’t believe in my own qualities?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.1788254124779,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sad-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 124.41215874581124
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "今は……信じることができないよ\nだって、あんなに簡単に揺らいじゃったんだもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That I’m unable to‚ right now.\nI mean‚ look how easily I wavered.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.1788254124779,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ミュージカルのことですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re talking about the musicals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.44549207914457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "……たぶん昔の私なら\nそれでもアイドルを続けるって言って聞かなかったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m pretty sure the old me\nwould’ve turned down the offer right off the bat.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.01215879349505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "でも今日、そういう道もありかもって揺らいじゃった\nそれはたぶん……自信がないからだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But today‚ I wavered‚ thinking that maybe that path is also an option\nThat’s probably because… I don’t have confidence.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.01215879349505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "自分で自分の、アイドルとしての素質を……\n今の私は、信じることができなくなってるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right now‚ I have a hard time believing\nin my own capabilities as an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.01215879349505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "なら、俺が信じますよ。俺だけじゃない、事務所の\nみんなも信じてる。それだけじゃ自信持てませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I’ll believe in you. Not just me‚ all the others in the agency\nbelieve in you as well. Is that not enough to give you confidence?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.312158793495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "……それって、具体的には？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "….Why exactly do you believe in me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.94549212682836,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "え？ ぐ、具体的にですか……？\nそうだな……まず何より、努力を重ねてきた時間？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? W-why exactly…?\nWell… first of all‚ the amount of time you spent working hard?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.7288254840036,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃ、みんなより年上だもん\n当たり前じゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I’m older than everyone‚\nWhy wouldn’t I?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.9724149928429,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "えっと……安定した歌唱力と\n一つ一つの動きが丁寧なダンス、ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Erm… Your vocals are very stable‚\nand you’re meticulous with each of your dance moves.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.40574832617617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_08_10-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "座長さんも同じこと言ってた\nやっぱりそっちの素質があるのかなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The head of the musical troupe said the same thing.\nMaybe my potential lies more in that direction.",
